| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3955 — Mass File Rename (lynx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 68aee87f-293d-5124-9c81-1bbe6122db4f"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
